'''Dušan J. Popović''' (1894&ndash;1985) was a [[Serbia]]n historian, a professor at the [[University of Belgrade]].
His works largely dealt with [[Serbs]] living in the 18th century outside of what latter would become known as the [[Serbia proper]].<ref>{{cite book | title = Dix années d'historiographie yougoslave 1945-1955 | author = Yugoslav National Committee for Historical Studies | editor = Jorjo Tadić | publisher = Maison d'edition "Jugoslavija," | year = 1955 | page = 109 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=aC0zAAAAMAA | accessdate = 2012-03-21}}</ref>
